Battles That Changed the World - 2nd Edition (2012).pdf Gooner

Publisher: Key Books Ltd (September 20, 2012)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 0946219338
ISBN-13: 978-0946219339

Following on from the first successful Battlefields Magazine
Against All Odds this second edition Battles that Changed the
World is about decisive battles that have altered the course of
history. This time the focus is on Hastings 1066, Waterloo in
1815 and Stalingrad 1942-3
